00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:04.764
LEONARD RAVICH WITH
AUDIENCE: Aah.

00:19:04.764 --> 00:19:05.970
LEONARD RAVICH: OK, you
can take your hand

00:19:05.970 --> 00:19:07.420
