00:28:53.370 --> 00:28:55.510
And the other one is
stay hungry, stay--

00:28:55.510 --> 00:28:56.380
AUDIENCE: --foolish.

00:28:56.380 --> 00:28:58.310
LEONARD RAVICH: Stay foolish.

00:28:58.310 --> 00:29:00.450
You do foolish things.

00:29:00.450 --> 00:29:03.110
As a matter of fact,
talk gibberish.

00:29:03.110 --> 00:29:05.280
Or just do something foolish,
like putting a little sticker

00:29:05.280 --> 00:29:08.380
on your car or your bicycle
that says I won the sperm

00:29:08.380 --> 00:29:11.220
race, and you've done it.

00:29:11.220 --> 00:29:12.120
And you feel better.

00:29:12.120 --> 00:29:13.750
And you have a good laugh.

00:29:13.750 --> 00:29:17.330
Before I go on, may I have a
round of applause, please?

00:29:17.330 --> 00:29:20.970
[APPLAUSE]

00:29:20.970 --> 00:29:24.560
LEONARD RAVICH: About 11 years
ago, I was sitting in a

00:29:24.560 --> 00:29:28.830
restaurant of a hotel that
I was staying at.

00:29:28.830 --> 00:29:31.740
And the waitress was
taking my order.

00:29:31.740 --> 00:29:35.020
And at the end, she said,
will that be all, sir?

00:29:35.020 --> 00:29:36.640
And I said, yes.

00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:39.140
And she said, thank
you, and left.

00:29:39.140 --> 00:29:41.980
Now, where I come from, I
never heard a waiter or

00:29:41.980 --> 00:29:44.440
waitress say to me "thank
you" by taking my order.

00:29:44.440 --> 00:29:47.480
Never happened.

00:29:47.480 --> 00:29:48.360
So I was curious.

00:29:48.360 --> 00:29:50.230
And so when she came
back, I said,

00:29:50.230 --> 00:29:51.510
can I ask you a question?

00:29:51.510 --> 00:29:55.600
Is it the policy of this hotel
for you to say to a guest

00:29:55.600 --> 00:29:58.120
"thank you" for taking
my order?

00:29:58.120 --> 00:30:01.280
And she said no, that's what
I got from my home.

00:30:01.280 --> 00:30:06.140
We were taught that if I have
a chance to serve someone,

00:30:06.140 --> 00:30:10.760
it's an opportunity for me
to get closer to God.

00:30:10.760 --> 00:30:12.110
I was stunned.

00:30:12.110 --> 00:30:13.850
She said, why did I say
thank you to you?

00:30:13.850 --> 00:30:16.140
Because you gave me an
opportunity to get closer to

00:30:16.140 --> 00:30:18.830
God by asking me to serve you.

00:30:18.830 --> 00:30:22.200
Now, why did this have
me in such a shock?

00:30:22.200 --> 00:30:24.430
Because it's the first time in
my life I had ever met a

00:30:24.430 --> 00:30:30.330
person who looks at service as
something godly or holy, that

00:30:30.330 --> 00:30:32.440
actually helping another person
or serving another

00:30:32.440 --> 00:30:36.120
person is a holy act.

00:30:36.120 --> 00:30:38.000
But you know what
she did for me--

00:30:38.000 --> 00:30:40.280
I thought about it-- and she
did it for you, too.

00:30:40.280 --> 00:30:44.130
She gave us what our purpose
and mission in life is.

00:30:44.130 --> 00:30:46.440
Our purpose and mission
in life is to serve.

00:30:46.440 --> 00:30:49.430
Think about what you
do every day.

00:30:49.430 --> 00:30:52.910
It's service, OK?

00:30:52.910 --> 00:30:55.790
Our purpose and mission in
life is to improve other

00:30:55.790 --> 00:30:57.150
people's lives.

00:30:57.150 --> 00:31:00.260
That's the whole reason around
Steve Jobs, Bill Gates.

00:31:00.260 --> 00:31:02.440
It's all about improving
people's lives.

00:31:02.440 --> 00:31:05.280
That's all they wanted to do.

00:31:05.280 --> 00:31:07.480
So our mission and purpose
in life is what?

00:31:07.480 --> 00:31:08.980
Its our meaning in life.

00:31:08.980 --> 00:31:10.590
Everybody needs a meaning.

00:31:10.590 --> 00:31:11.710
Let me just tell you
how important

00:31:11.710 --> 00:31:14.020
meaning is in your life.

00:31:14.020 --> 00:31:19.440
If anybody's ever read a book
called "Man's Search for

00:31:19.440 --> 00:31:26.920
Meaning" by Dr. Frankel, Victor
Frankel, he says that

00:31:26.920 --> 00:31:30.690
in order to have meaning in
our lives, it gives us the

00:31:30.690 --> 00:31:35.890
reason to live, the reason to
live, to have meaning, OK?

00:31:35.890 --> 00:31:37.910
And if your meaning is service,
if your meaning is

00:31:37.910 --> 00:31:39.880
helping other people, improving
other people's

00:31:39.880 --> 00:31:42.500
lives, that gives you
a meaning in life.

00:31:42.500 --> 00:31:45.790
And I want to just tell
you one little story

